N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 34.2 - Grades of new york cheese

State Regulations

Two grades of cheddar cheese, washed curd cheese and colby
cheese manufactured in New York State are hereby established: namely "New York

State Brand" and "New York Standard."
